data.description: This lovely four-bedroom, one and a half bath ranch style home is located in the desirable Park Layne Manor neighborhood. With a partially fenced backyard, you'll have privacy and space to enjoy the outdoors. The home offers just over 1500 square feet of living area, providing ample room for your family. The wood burner adds a cozy and inviting touch, This home has been well maintained, Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming property your own!
